    "skill1": {
      "name": "Crash Course",
      "description": "Chip rams his hovercraft into the ground, dealing (Magic Damage) equal to 150 plus 5% of target's Max HP and applying (Chip's Mark) on enemy heroes hit. Chip gains a 300( +60% Total Magic Power) Shield upon hitting an enemy hero, which increases by 25% for each additional enemy hero hit. Chip's next Basic Attack will become ranged and also hit all nearby enemies with (Chip's Mark), detonating the mark to deal 200( +40% Total Magic Power) (Magic Damage) and stun each target for 0.6s.",
